I have the charm of the brother hood, got lucky got every piece all in one night. Just watch for /ooc of rotting stuff and its easy. Cool thing I found out is that now after a recent patch they made it to where its stats turn on when you are grouped with a member of the same class AND/OR race. This is a good thing, because what does every bard have a fetish of collecting? Illusion masks. Yes with an illusion mask on it fools the charm into thinking that you are that race so the charm's stats get activated. So in a way thats a good charm for bards.</span></td>
